# This file contains the key mappings for Gaia Sky.

# Each line contains an action=keys pair, where action is the
# action id and keys is a list of keys to map to the action.
# If you need to map more than one key combination to the same
# action, just repeat the same action more than once.

# Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.

